"totaux et le calendrier d'amortissement. Calculez les coûts du prêt "
"immobilier, y compris la taxe foncière, l'assurance, le PMI et les frais "
"HOA."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"mortgage calculator, home loan calculator, monthly payment calculator, "
"amortization schedule, PMI calculator, property tax calculator, PITI "
"calculator"
msgstr ""
"calculateur d'hypothèque, calculateur de prêt immobilier, calculateur de "
"mensualités, calendrier d'amortissement, calculateur PMI, calculateur "
"d'impôt foncier, calculateur PITI"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Home Loan Payments"
msgstr "Calculer les paiements du prêt immobilier"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate monthly mortgage payments with taxes, insurance, and PMI. View "
"amortization schedule and see how extra payments save money."
msgstr ""
"Calculez les versements hypothécaires mensuels avec les taxes, les "
"assurances et le PMI. Consultez le calendrier d’amortissement et voyez "
"comment les paiements supplémentaires permettent d’économiser de l’argent."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:21
msgid "Free mortgage payment calculator with amortization schedule."
msgstr ""
"Calculateur de versements hypothécaires gratuit avec calendrier "
"d'amortissement."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:28
msgid "Calculate monthly mortgage payments with taxes, insurance, and PMI"
msgstr ""
"Calculez les versements hypothécaires mensuels avec les taxes, l'assurance "
"et le PMI"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:43
msgid "What is included in a monthly mortgage payment?"
msgstr "Qu’est-ce qui est inclus dans un versement hypothécaire mensuel ?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:46
msgid ""
"A monthly mortgage payment typically includes Principal (loan amount), "
"Interest, Property Taxes, Homeowners Insurance (PITI), and sometimes PMI and"
" HOA fees."
msgstr ""
"Un versement hypothécaire mensuel comprend généralement le capital (montant "
"du prêt), les intérêts, les taxes foncières, l'assurance habitation (PITI) "
"et parfois les frais PMI et HOA."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:51
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:481
msgid "What is PMI and when is it required?"
msgstr "Qu’est-ce que le PMI et quand est-il nécessaire ?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:54
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Private Mortgage Insurance (PMI) is typically required when your down "
"payment is less than 20%% of the home price. PMI protects the lender if you "
"default on the loan."
msgstr ""
"L'assurance hypothécaire privée (PMI) est généralement requise lorsque votre"
" mise de fonds est inférieure à 20 % du prix de la maison. PMI protège le "
"prêteur si vous ne remboursez pas le prêt."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:59
msgid "How can I lower my monthly mortgage payment?"
msgstr "Comment puis-je réduire mes mensualités hypothécaires ?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:62
msgid ""
"You can lower your payment by: making a larger down payment, choosing a "
"longer loan term, shopping for lower interest rates, or buying a less "
"expensive home."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez réduire votre paiement en effectuant une mise de fonds plus "
"importante, en choisissant une durée de prêt plus longue, en recherchant des"
" taux d'intérêt plus bas ou en achetant une maison moins chère."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:89
msgid ""
"Calculate your monthly mortgage payment including principal, interest, "
"taxes, insurance, and PMI."
msgstr ""
"Calculez votre versement hypothécaire mensuel, y compris le capital, les "
"intérêts, les taxes, l'assurance et le PMI."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:115
