msgstr "Qu’est-ce que le rythme de course ?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:313
msgid ""
"Running pace is the time it takes to cover a specific distance, typically "
"expressed as minutes per kilometer (min/km) or minutes per mile (min/mi). "
"It's a fundamental metric for runners to track performance, plan training, "
"and predict race times."
msgstr ""
"Le rythme de course est le temps nécessaire pour parcourir une distance "
"spécifique, généralement exprimé en minutes par kilomètre (min/km) ou en "
"minutes par mile (min/mi). Il s'agit d'une mesure fondamentale permettant "
"aux coureurs de suivre leurs performances, de planifier leur entraînement et"
" de prédire les temps de course."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:316
msgid "Pace = Time ÷ Distance"
msgstr "Allure = Temps ÷ Distance"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:319
msgid ""
"For example, if you run 5 kilometers in 30 minutes, your pace is 6 minutes "
"per kilometer (30 ÷ 5 = 6 min/km)."
msgstr ""
"Par exemple, si vous courez 5 kilomètres en 30 minutes, votre allure est de "
"6 minutes par kilomètre (30 ÷ 5 = 6 min/km)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:325
msgid "Pace Categories"
msgstr "Catégories de rythme"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:328
msgid "Elite: &lt; 3:30 min/km"
msgstr "Élite : &Lt ; 3h30 mn/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:330
msgid "World-class performance. Professional and elite competitive runners."
msgstr ""
"Des performances de classe mondiale. Coureurs de compétition professionnels "
"et élites."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:334
msgid "Advanced: 3:30-4:00 min/km"
msgstr "Avancé : 3h30-4h00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:336
msgid ""
"Excellent performance. Highly trained runners with years of experience."
msgstr ""
"Excellente performance. Coureurs hautement qualifiés avec des années "
"d’expérience."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:340
msgid "Intermediate: 4:00-5:00 min/km"
msgstr "Intermédiaire : 4h00-5h00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:342
msgid "Good fitness level. Regular runners with consistent training."
msgstr ""
"Bon niveau de forme physique. Coureurs réguliers avec un entraînement "
"constant."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:346
msgid "Recreational: 5:00-6:00 min/km"
msgstr "Récréatif : 5h00-6h00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:348
msgid "Healthy activity level. Casual runners maintaining fitness."
msgstr ""
"Niveau d'activité sain. Coureurs occasionnels qui maintiennent leur forme "
"physique."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:352
msgid "Beginner: 6:00-7:00 min/km"
msgstr "Débutant : 6h00-7h00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:354
msgid "Building fitness. New runners or those returning to running."
msgstr ""
"Construire la forme physique. Les nouveaux coureurs ou ceux qui recommencent"
" à courir."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:358
msgid "Walking: &gt; 7:00 min/km"
msgstr "Marche : &gt; 7h00 minutes/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:360
msgid "Walking pace. Great for health, recovery, and active rest."
msgstr ""
"Rythme de marche. Idéal pour la santé, la récupération et le repos actif."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:370
msgid "Select calculation type: 'Pace from Time' or 'Time from Pace'"
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez le type de calcul : « Rythme à partir du temps » ou « Temps à "
"partir du rythme »"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:371
msgid "Choose your distance unit (kilometers or miles)"
msgstr "Choisissez votre unité de distance (kilomètres ou miles)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:372
msgid "Enter your distance and time (or pace)"
msgstr "Entrez votre distance et votre temps (ou votre allure)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:374
msgid "Review your pace, speed, and race time predictions"
msgstr ""
"Passez en revue vos prévisions d'allure, de vitesse et de temps de course"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:375
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your performance"
msgstr "Utilisez les graphiques pour visualiser vos performances"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:384
msgid "Pace per Kilometer/Mile"
msgstr "Allure par kilomètre/mile"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"The time it takes to run one kilometer or one mile. Lower numbers mean "
"faster pace. Displayed as minutes:seconds per unit distance."
msgstr ""
"Le temps qu'il faut pour courir un kilomètre ou un mile. Des chiffres plus "
"faibles signifient un rythme plus rapide. Affiché en minutes : secondes par "
"unité de distance."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:390
msgid "Speed (km/h or mph)"
msgstr "Vitesse (km/h ou mph)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:392
msgid ""
"Your average running speed. Calculated as distance divided by time. Useful "
"for comparing with other activities like cycling or driving."
msgstr ""
"Votre vitesse de course moyenne. Calculé comme la distance divisée par le "
"temps. Utile pour comparer avec d’autres activités comme le vélo ou la "
"conduite automobile."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:398
msgid ""
"Estimated finish times for common race distances (1km, 5km, 10km, half "
"marathon, marathon) based on your current pace. Useful for goal setting and "
"race planning."
msgstr ""
"Temps d'arrivée estimés pour les distances de course courantes (1 km, 5 km, "
"10 km, semi-marathon, marathon) en fonction de votre rythme actuel. Utile "
"pour l’établissement d’objectifs et la planification de courses."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:406
msgid "Training Tips"
msgstr "Conseils de formation"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:409
msgid "Consistent Training"
msgstr "Formation cohérente"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:411
msgid ""
"Regular running improves pace over time. Aim for 3-4 runs per week with "
"gradual distance increases."
msgstr ""
"Courir régulièrement améliore le rythme au fil du temps. Visez 3 à 4 courses"
" par semaine avec des augmentations progressives de la distance."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:415
msgid "Interval Training"
msgstr "Entraînement par intervalles"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:417
msgid ""
"Incorporate speed work (intervals, tempo runs) to improve pace. Mix fast and"
" slow runs for balanced training."
msgstr ""
"Incorporez un travail de vitesse (intervalles, courses rythmées) pour "
"améliorer le rythme. Mélangez des courses rapides et lentes pour un "
"entraînement équilibré."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:421
msgid "Recovery"
msgstr "Récupération"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:423
msgid ""
"Allow adequate rest between hard runs. Recovery is essential for improvement"
" and injury prevention."
msgstr ""
"Prévoyez un repos adéquat entre les courses difficiles. La récupération est "
"essentielle à l’amélioration et à la prévention des blessures."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Pace varies with terrain, weather, elevation, and fitness level. Use this "
"calculator as a guide, not an absolute measure."
msgstr ""
"Le rythme varie en fonction du terrain, de la météo, de l'altitude et du "
"niveau de forme physique. Utilisez cette calculatrice comme guide et non "
"comme mesure absolue."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:443
msgid ""
"Race time predictions assume you can maintain the same pace for longer "
"distances, which may not always be realistic. Adjust expectations based on "
"your training."
msgstr ""
"Les prévisions de temps de course supposent que vous pouvez maintenir le "
"même rythme sur de plus longues distances, ce qui n'est pas toujours "
"réaliste. Ajustez les attentes en fonction de votre formation."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:449
msgid ""
"For accurate pace tracking, use GPS watches, running apps, or measured "
"courses. Manual calculations are estimates."
msgstr ""
"Pour un suivi précis du rythme, utilisez des montres GPS, des applications "
"en cours d'exécution ou des parcours mesurés. Les calculs manuels sont des "
"estimations."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:455
msgid ""
"Always listen to your body. If you experience pain or excessive fatigue, "
"rest and consult with healthcare professionals."
msgstr ""
"Écoutez toujours votre corps. Si vous ressentez des douleurs ou une fatigue "
"excessive, reposez-vous et consultez des professionnels de la santé."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:631
msgid "1 km"
msgstr "1km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:632
msgid "5 km"
msgstr "5km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:633
msgid "10 km"
msgstr "10km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:634
msgid "Half Marathon"
msgstr "Semi-marathon"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:635
msgid "Marathon"
msgstr "Marathon"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:677
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:642
#: Other_Calculators/views/hours_calculator.py:807
msgid "Total Time"
msgstr "Durée totale"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:48
msgid "Period Calculator"
msgstr "Calculateur de période"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:14
msgid "Menstrual Cycle Tracker"
msgstr "Suivi du cycle menstruel"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period. Free period "
"calculator with ovulation and fertile window predictions."
msgstr ""
"Suivez votre cycle menstruel et prédisez vos prochaines règles. Calculateur "
"de règles gratuit avec prévisions d'ovulation et de fenêtre fertile."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"period calculator, menstrual cycle calculator, period tracker, ovulation "
"calculator, fertile window"
msgstr ""
"calculateur de règles, calculateur de cycle menstruel, suivi des règles, "
"calculateur d'ovulation, fenêtre fertile"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:15
msgid "Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period dates."
msgstr ""
"Suivez votre cycle menstruel et prédisez vos prochaines dates de règles."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:24
msgid "Track menstrual cycle and predict next period dates"
msgstr "Suivez le cycle menstruel et prédisez les dates des prochaines règles"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period dates, ovulation, "
"and fertile window. Get comprehensive cycle analysis and personalized "
"predictions."
msgstr ""
"Suivez votre cycle menstruel et prédisez vos prochaines dates de règles, "
"votre ovulation et votre fenêtre fertile. Obtenez une analyse complète du "
"cycle et des prédictions personnalisées."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:73
msgid "Last Period Start Date"
msgstr "Date de début de la dernière période"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:94
msgid "Period Length"
msgstr "Durée de la période"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:101
msgid "Range: 2-7 days (average: 5 days)"
msgstr "Plage : 2 à 7 jours (moyenne : 5 jours)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:145
msgid ""
"Enter your cycle information to see predictions for your next periods, "
"ovulation dates, fertile windows, and comprehensive cycle analysis."
msgstr ""
"Entrez les informations de votre cycle pour voir les prévisions de vos "
"prochaines règles, les dates d'ovulation, les fenêtres fertiles et une "
"analyse complète du cycle."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:168
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:372
msgid "Current Cycle Day"
msgstr "Jour de cycle en cours"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:175
msgid "Days Until Period"
msgstr "Jours avant la période"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:181
msgid "Days Until Ovulation"
msgstr "Jours avant l'ovulation"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:193
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/date_calculator.html:92
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_counter.html:90
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:149
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:179
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:149
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:179
msgid "Start Date"
msgstr "Date de début"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:203
msgid "Ovulation & Fertile Window"
msgstr "Ovulation et fenêtre fertile"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:238
msgid "Cycle Progress"
msgstr "Progression du cycle"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:252
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:261
msgid "Upcoming Cycles"
msgstr "Cycles à venir"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:290
msgid "What is the Menstrual Cycle?"
msgstr "Qu'est-ce que le cycle menstruel ?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:292
msgid ""
"The menstrual cycle is a natural process that occurs in the female "
"reproductive system, typically lasting 21-35 days (average 28 days). It "
"involves hormonal changes that prepare the body for potential pregnancy each"
" month."
msgstr ""
"Le cycle menstruel est un processus naturel qui se produit dans le système "
"reproducteur féminin et dure généralement de 21 à 35 jours (en moyenne 28 "
"jours). Cela implique des changements hormonaux qui préparent le corps à une"
" éventuelle grossesse chaque mois."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:295
msgid ""
"The cycle begins on the first day of menstruation (period) and ends the day "
"before the next period starts. Understanding your cycle helps with fertility"
" planning, health monitoring, and predicting period dates."
msgstr ""
"Le cycle commence le premier jour des règles (règles) et se termine la "
"veille du début des règles suivantes. Comprendre votre cycle aide à "
"planifier la fertilité, à surveiller la santé et à prédire les dates des "
"règles."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"Enter your average period length (how many days your period typically lasts)"
msgstr ""
"Entrez la durée moyenne de vos règles (combien de jours durent généralement "
"vos règles)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Click 'Calculate' to see predictions for your next periods, ovulation dates,"
" and fertile windows"
msgstr ""
"Cliquez sur « Calculer » pour voir les prévisions de vos prochaines règles, "
"les dates d'ovulation et les fenêtres fertiles."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:344
msgid "Review the cycle calendar and phase distribution charts"
msgstr ""
"Consultez le calendrier des cycles et les tableaux de répartition des "
"phases."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:345
msgid "Use the predictions to plan ahead and track your cycle"
msgstr ""
"Utilisez les prédictions pour planifier à l'avance et suivre votre cycle"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:356
msgid ""
"Predicted start and end dates for your next menstrual period based on your "
"cycle length and last period date."
msgstr ""
"Dates prévues de début et de fin de vos prochaines règles en fonction de la "
"durée de votre cycle et de la date de vos dernières règles."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"Estimated date when ovulation occurs (typically 14 days before your next "
"period). This is your most fertile day."
msgstr ""
"Date estimée de l'ovulation (généralement 14 jours avant vos prochaines "
"règles). C'est votre jour le plus fertile."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception is most likely. This includes 5 days "
"before ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after."
msgstr ""
"La période de 6 à 7 jours pendant laquelle la conception est la plus "
"probable. Cela comprend 5 jours avant l'ovulation, le jour de l'ovulation et"
" 1 jour après."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"Shows which day of your current cycle you are on. Day 1 is the first day of "
"your last period."
msgstr ""
"Indique à quel jour de votre cycle actuel vous vous trouvez. Le jour 1 est "
"le premier jour de vos dernières règles."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:382
msgid "Cycle Tracking Tips"
msgstr "Conseils pour le suivi du cycle"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:385
msgid "Consistent Tracking"
msgstr "Suivi cohérent"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:387
msgid ""
"Track your period start dates for at least 3-6 months to get an accurate "
"average cycle length. Mark dates on a calendar or use a period tracking app."
msgstr ""
"Suivez les dates de début de vos règles pendant au moins 3 à 6 mois pour "
"obtenir une durée moyenne précise du cycle. Marquez les dates sur un "
"calendrier ou utilisez une application de suivi des règles."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:391
msgid "Note Symptoms"
msgstr "Remarque Symptômes"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"Track symptoms like cramps, mood changes, and flow intensity. This helps "
"identify patterns and can be useful for healthcare consultations."
msgstr ""
"Suivez les symptômes tels que les crampes, les changements d’humeur et "
"l’intensité du flux. Cela permet d’identifier des modèles et peut être utile"
" pour les consultations médicales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:397
msgid "Irregular Cycles"
msgstr "Cycles irréguliers"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:399
msgid ""
"If your cycles are very irregular (varying by more than 7 days), consider "
"consulting with a healthcare provider. Irregular cycles can indicate "
"underlying health conditions."
msgstr ""
"Si vos cycles sont très irréguliers (variant de plus de 7 jours), envisagez "
"de consulter un professionnel de santé. Des cycles irréguliers peuvent "
"indiquer des problèmes de santé sous-jacents."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Period calculators provide estimates based on average cycle patterns. Actual"
" timing can vary due to stress, illness, travel, hormonal changes, or "
"medical conditions."
msgstr ""
"Les calculateurs de périodes fournissent des estimations basées sur des "
"modèles de cycle moyens. Le moment réel peut varier en raison du stress, de "
"la maladie, des voyages, des changements hormonaux ou de conditions "
"médicales."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"If you have irregular cycles, PCOS, endometriosis, or other reproductive "
"health concerns, consult with a healthcare provider or gynecologist for "
"personalized guidance."
msgstr ""
"Si vous avez des cycles irréguliers, un SOPK, une endométriose ou d'autres "
"problèmes de santé reproductive, consultez un professionnel de la santé ou "
"un gynécologue pour obtenir des conseils personnalisés."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult healthcare providers for "
"reproductive health concerns, fertility planning, or if you experience "
"unusual symptoms."
msgstr ""
"Ce calculateur est fourni à titre informatif uniquement et ne doit pas "
"remplacer un avis médical professionnel. Consultez toujours les prestataires"
" de soins de santé pour des problèmes de santé reproductive, de "
"planification de la fertilité ou si vous ressentez des symptômes "
"inhabituels."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:556
msgid "complete"
msgstr "complet"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:608
msgid "Cycle"
msgstr "Faire du vélo"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:611
msgid "Period"
msgstr "Période"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:615
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:364
msgid "Ovulation"
