msgstr "Besoins en protéines par objectif de forme physique"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:432
#, python-format
msgid "Weight Loss (+20%%)"
msgstr "Perte de poids (+20%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Higher protein intake helps preserve muscle mass during calorie deficit and "
"increases satiety, making it easier to stick to your diet."
msgstr ""
"Un apport plus élevé en protéines aide à préserver la masse musculaire en "
"cas de déficit calorique et augmente la satiété, facilitant ainsi le respect"
" de son régime."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:438
msgid "Maintain Weight (Standard)"
msgstr "Maintenir le poids (standard)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:440
msgid ""
"Standard protein intake to maintain current muscle mass and support daily "
"activities and recovery."
msgstr ""
"Apport standard en protéines pour maintenir la masse musculaire actuelle et "
"soutenir les activités quotidiennes et la récupération."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:444
#, python-format
msgid "Muscle Gain (+10%%)"
msgstr "Gain musculaire (+10%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:446
msgid ""
"Slightly higher protein intake to support muscle growth and recovery from "
"training. Essential for building new muscle tissue."
msgstr ""
"Apport légèrement plus élevé en protéines pour soutenir la croissance "
"musculaire et la récupération après l'entraînement. Indispensable pour "
"construire de nouveaux tissus musculaires."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:450
#, python-format
msgid "Cutting (+30%%)"
msgstr "Découpe (+30%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"High protein intake to preserve muscle mass during aggressive fat loss "
"phase. Critical for bodybuilders and athletes cutting weight."
msgstr ""
"Apport élevé en protéines pour préserver la masse musculaire lors des phases"
" agressives de perte de graisse. Essentiel pour les bodybuilders et les "
"athlètes qui perdent du poids."

