#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:36
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:41
msgid "Bandwidth Calculator - Free Online Tool"
msgstr "Calculateur de bande passante - Outil en ligne gratuit"

