#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:283
msgid "What is a Day Of The Week Calculator?"
msgstr "Qu'est-ce qu'un calculateur de jour de la semaine ?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:285
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:285
msgid ""
"A day of week calculator is a tool that determines what day of the week any "
"date falls on, finds the next or previous occurrence of a specific weekday, "
"and counts how many times a weekday appears in a date range. This calculator"
" uses precise date arithmetic to handle all calendar complexities including "
"leap years and varying month lengths."
msgstr ""
"Un calculateur de jour de la semaine est un outil qui détermine le jour de "
"la semaine auquel tombe une date, trouve l'occurrence suivante ou précédente"
" d'un jour de la semaine spécifique et compte combien de fois un jour de la "
"semaine apparaît dans une plage de dates. Cette calculatrice utilise une "
"arithmétique de date précise pour gérer toutes les complexités du "
"calendrier, y compris les années bissextiles et les différentes durées de "
"mois."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:292
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:292
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Find Day of Week, Next "
"Occurrence, Previous Occurrence, Count Weekdays, or Find All Occurrences)."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez un type de calcul dans la liste déroulante (Rechercher le jour "
"de la semaine, Prochaine occurrence, Occurrence précédente, Compter les "
"jours de la semaine ou Rechercher toutes les occurrences)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:293
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:293
msgid "Enter the required dates and weekday information in the input form."
msgstr ""
"Entrez les dates requises et les informations sur les jours de la semaine "
"dans le formulaire de saisie."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:305
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:305
msgid ""
"Enter any date to find what day of the week it falls on. Also shows if it's "
"a weekday or weekend."
msgstr ""
"Entrez n’importe quelle date pour savoir à quel jour de la semaine elle "
"tombe. Indique également si c'est un jour de semaine ou un week-end."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:309
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:309
msgid ""
"Find the next occurrence of a specific weekday (e.g., next Monday) from a "
"given date."
msgstr ""
"Recherchez la prochaine occurrence d'un jour de la semaine spécifique (par "
"exemple, lundi prochain) à partir d'une date donnée."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:313
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:313
msgid ""
"Find the previous occurrence of a specific weekday (e.g., last Friday) from "
"a given date."
msgstr ""
"Recherchez l'occurrence précédente d'un jour de la semaine spécifique (par "
"exemple, vendredi dernier) à partir d'une date donnée."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:317
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:317
msgid ""
"Count how many times a specific weekday occurs in a date range. Includes "
"visualization."
msgstr ""
"Comptez combien de fois un jour de la semaine spécifique apparaît dans une "
"plage de dates. Comprend la visualisation."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:321
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:321
msgid ""
"Find all dates in a range that fall on a specific weekday. Lists up to 20 "
"occurrences."
msgstr ""
"Recherchez toutes les dates d’une plage correspondant à un jour de semaine "
"spécifique. Répertorie jusqu'à 20 occurrences."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:327
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:327
msgid "Understanding Weekdays"
msgstr "Comprendre les jours de la semaine"

