msgid "GPA Scales"
msgstr "Échelles GPA"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:240
msgid "Most common scale in the United States. A+ and A both equal 4.0."
msgstr ""
"Échelle la plus courante aux États-Unis. A+ et A sont tous deux égaux à 4,0."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:244
msgid ""
"Used by some institutions. A+ equals 4.3, allowing for higher distinction."
msgstr ""
"Utilisé par certaines institutions. A+ est égal à 4,3, ce qui permet une "
